title: Your Life at Level 10

description:
Episode 603 - On a scale of 1 to 10, what level are you living your life at right now? A level 5? Level 6? Level 7? How much different would your life look if you lived at a level 10? Well in this episode, we will dive into that topic and I will teach you how to live at a level 10 today!   Are you ready to break out of your comfort zone? If so, join the Iron Mind 60 Challenge here www.IronMind60.com
